&lt;li&gt;Lead the planning and execution of integrated, multi-channel annual giving campaigns—including direct mail, email, digital fundraising, and giving day initiatives—to drive donor acquisition, retention, and revenue growth in support of annual fund goals.&lt;/li&gt;
